ZH: 我这个周末要去参加一个法事。
EN: I will attend a funeral this weekend.
ZH: 法事是中国文化中一种很重要的仪式。
EN: Funerals are an important ritual in Chinese culture.
ZH: 我们要为祖先举行一场盛大的法事。
EN: We are going to hold a grand funeral for our ancestors.
ZH: 祖父母去世后，我们每年都会为他们举办法事。
EN: After our grandparents passed away, we hold a funeral for them every year.
ZH: 法事期间，亲友们会一起祭拜逝者。
EN: During the funeral, relatives and friends gather to pay tribute to the deceased.
ZH: 法事中会进行一系列的宗教仪式。
EN: A series of religious rituals are performed during the funeral.
ZH: 我会在法事上念诵经文。
EN: I will recite scriptures during the funeral.
ZH: 法事是对逝者的一种告别仪式。
EN: Funerals are a farewell ceremony for the deceased.
ZH: 这次法事是为了追念我的亲人。
EN: This funeral is to commemorate my loved one.
ZH: 法事后，我们会举行一个纪念活动。
EN: After the funeral, we will have a memorial event.
ZH: 法事上要穿着朴素，不宜穿得过于华丽。
EN: It is advisable to dress modestly for a funeral, avoiding overly glamorous attire.
ZH: 许多人会送上花圈或凋零的白菊花参加法事。
EN: Many people bring wreaths or withered white chrysanthemums to the funeral.
ZH: 法事上，亲友们都会为逝者送上最后一程。
EN: During the funeral, relatives and friends accompany the deceased for their final journey.
ZH: 法事是一个庄重而严肃的场合。
EN: Funerals are solemn and serious occasions.
ZH: 法事上期间，大家都要保持沉默和庄重。
EN: It is important to maintain silence and solemnity during the funeral.
ZH: 法事上，亲友们会为逝者祈福。
EN: Relatives and friends will pray for the deceased during the funeral.
ZH: 法事上我会表达我对逝者的敬意。
EN: I will express my respect for the deceased during the funeral.
ZH: 法事结束后，我们会为逝者安葬。
EN: After the funeral, we will bury the deceased.
ZH: 法事过后，家人会为逝者守孝一段时间。
EN: After the funeral, the family will observe a period of mourning for the deceased.
ZH: 法事是一个让人感到悲伤的时刻。
EN: Funerals are a moment of sadness.
